Package net.consensys.cava.bytes

Classes and utilities for working with byte arrays.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Bytes
    A value made of bytes.
    Bytes32
    A Bytes value that is guaranteed to contain exactly 32 bytes.
    MutableBytes
    A mutable Bytes value.
    MutableBytes32
    A mutable Bytes32, that is a mutable Bytes value of exactly 32 bytes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBytes
    An abstract Bytes value that provides implementations of AbstractBytes.equals(Object), AbstractBytes.hashCode() and AbstractBytes.toString().
    MutableByteBufferWrappingBytes  

Package net.consensys.cava.bytes Description

Classes and utilities for working with byte arrays.

These classes are included in the standard Cava distribution, or separately when using the gradle dependency 'net.consensys.cava:cava-bytes' (cava-bytes.jar).
